com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"4b62be325d2afb30ff684fd855c0d3ea093f1c5e","tid":1462420,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"咪阻啦"},{"pid":"0e8c5a1ccf46803ff33081d09a1f0535c5551e85","tid":1462420,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"輸出革命"},{"pid":"c3487588e36f0e7bdd9e42785041ff7bc84a186e","tid":1462420,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"感謝 <br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"055c42aa1070633388337b239ae076ea8fe77cf9","tid":1462420,"uid":277702,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，將革命因子種落去支那客度唔得嘅？屌你老味共匪喺大陸裏面就係咁宣傳香港有幾撚亂有幾撚多暴徒⋯⋯屌你而家即係話比班支那客聽共匪講嘅嘢係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac959615e01fb08a463d10f5fc2485e993fe7f87","tid":1462420,"uid":206284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"果堆支那人airdrop下d文宣比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b583139efeee87106a99be935992fca4eb0cc5","tid":1462420,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"257fc140bf77ce2994c0a54b416a0b2df24856c9","tid":1462420,"uid":94824,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3b9edf97ea6272b87c31c76e2d172e24990ca824","tid":1462420,"uid":23088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"T2有條後樓梯可以落下一層<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經將有老有嫩的外國旅客送晒落去(支那人除外)</span></span><br /